STEP|42|Doctor output:**
STEP|43|Check: which code-review-graph → if found, features.codeReviewGraph = true
STEP|44|If missing: check pip → pip install code-review-graph → code-review-graph build
STEP|45|Fallback: built-in regex graph builder (always works, zero deps)
STEP|46|Reads `~/.hermes/memories/USER.md` and `MEMORY.md`
